  "detailed_description": "****************************************************************<br>**** If you ran into an issue, or have any feedback, <br>**** please join this discord channel and send us a message: (we'll respond faster this way)<br>**** <br>****************************************************************<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/c1ea036b02a70e853944ce95f938f1af.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=126 /></span><br>This is a perfect hybrid of a social board game and strategy card game.<br>You play as a pirate... adventurer in the Age of Discovery, heading into the lost islands along <br>side three other adventurers. As you dive deeper and deeper into the adventure, things become<br>more dangerous and enticing, only the bravest and smartest can take the treasure out alive. <br>You'll make many different hard choices during the adventure: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Continue for more or escape with what you have?<br></li><li>Co-operate with other players or stabs them in the back?<br></li><li>Prepare for the incoming danger or risk for more reward?</li></ul>You'll find your answers in the Journey of Greed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/5626e976f5f1b4ab8f1c8f575e6755e7.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Share Less</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/38449aac498f485768b80a5737d7c0bb.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=306 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take a Little </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/fc267764f0f893f506fbfc7d28941314.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=285 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hit and Run</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/5ad7bce4bb0f91d5c017c1003ff56a8a.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=305 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Self Provide </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/bc885f966fa4bf350d6abc261034a2be.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=305 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/e1b8ceea4f5101723f9c325a5a80fad2.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/4aaea6e90cd0e544d784834aca10b9fb.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1032790/extras/eaf58bcc288c64a4bb8e59aac835ab67.avif?t=1660894633\" width=616 height=128 /></span><br><br>Difference between the demo and full version: <br>1. You can only open 10 “Barrels” in the demo.<br>2. You can't play Ladder mode after passing Rookie in the Demo<br>3. The demo and full version share the same server, so your data will persist once you get the full version.",
